name: F1=-F2
description:
This is our submission for the GamJamSummit 2022

Devs: 

Quentin Sebac-Henry / Tyran#0716

niklas7986#7393

Both underaged (16 and 17)

The game is a small Puzzle Platformer with several fun mechanics. The game had to be made in only 2 days because of personal time restrictions and thus is not very polished. There is a very small story so please play the game with sound on as it is inportant for progression in the levels. 

If you are stuck in a level you can press 0 to skip to the end of the level.

Have fun
